<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٥١٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3654">الْحُمَيْدِيُّ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">سُفْيَانُ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6702">هِشَامٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5064">فَاطِمَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/622">أَسْمَاءَ </a>قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«نَحَرْنَا فَرَسًا عَلَى عَهْدِ رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَأَكَلْنَاهُ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>